title: Karin Legemate
text:
Katarina Johanna Agatha Legemate is a Dutch former <a href="women%27s%20soccer">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a>. Throughout her career she played for <a href="Ter%20Leede">Ter Leede</a> in the pre-2007 <a href="Hoofdklasse%20%28women%29">Hoofdklasse</a> and <a href="ADO%20Den%20Haag">ADO Den Haag</a> and <a href="AZ%20%28women%27s%20football%20club%29">AZ</a> in the <a href="Eredivisie%20%28women%29">Eredivisie</a>. She retired in 2011 following AZ's disbandment.
She was a member of the <a href="Netherlands%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Dutch national team</a> and played 22 matches between her debut on 5 February 2006 against <a href="Finland%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Finland</a> and her last match on 8 August 2009 against <a href="Poland%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Poland</a>.
